	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bards is a lot of fun. You get bored if you just tank. With a bard you can do everything. Solo or don't, you can do it all. If you get bored with one tactic, switch, try something new.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can do that with a bard without creating a new character.<br>Con is surely that it isn't stats that make a bard a good char. It is how well you use your abilities. Switch songs at the right time, twist songs, know when to fight, when to support, ... it's a bit hard as a starting character since you have to know the keys, commands and macros help a lot.<br>Go for the bard if you want more than slashing machine...<br><br>Wara "Merry Fairytune"<br>Wood Elf Bard<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
