	   <tr><td colspan=2>This sound very trivial but, I also have a hot-key for a inventory slot and leave a bag in that slot with all of my instruments and weapons :).&nbsp;&nbsp;Sounds silly but, you can open the bag during a fight.  It will stay open and it is easy to change out multiple instruments/weapons.<br><br>Just a thought.<br><br>Rluile<br>24th Bard<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
